<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5835953>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Impatiens jurpia var. ravikumareana Tiwari, U.L. var. nov. A. Habit. B. Leaf dorsal surface. C. Portion of leaf petiole with pelted glands. D. Side view of flower bud; E. Side view of mature flower. F. Mature flower-front view. G. Lateral sepals. H. Lower sepal with spur. I. Lateral united petals-ventral view. J. Dorsal petal-ventral view. K. Immature Clavate fruit. L. Stamens (Photos by U.L. Tiwari)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5835953/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5835955>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Impatiens jurpia var. ravikumareana Tiwari, U.L. var. nov. A. Habit. B. Flower bud-side view. C. Mature flower-front view; D. Lower sepal with spur. E. Dorsal petal. F. Lateral united petals (Illustration by U.L. Tiwari)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5835955/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

